"title": "5896: irreverence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5896: irreverence",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A complete absence of the proper sense of awe, respect and wonder that is inspired and demanded by the character and activity of the living God. Irreverence involves disrespect for the character, deeds, words, law and ministers of God. As such, it brings judgment upon those who behave in this way.</p>\n<h2>Irreverence as the root of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:10\">ROM 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:18\">ROM 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:1\">PSA 36:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4-Ps10:5\">PSA 10:4–10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:19\">PSA 55:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion leads to irreverence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:23-Jer5:24\">JER 5:23–5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:3-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:3–15:9</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of irreverence</h2>\n<h3>Arrogance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4-Ps10:5\">PSA 10:4–10:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:19-Deut17:20\">DEU 17:19–17:20</a></p>\n<h3>Self-deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:1-Ps36:2\">PSA 36:1–36:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:9\">PRO 30:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4-Ps10:5\">PSA 10:4–10:5</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of irreverence</h2>\n<h3>Insulting God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:9\">PSA 69:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:22-Ps74:23\">PSA 74:22–74:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>Misusing God's name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:10-Lev24:16\">LEV 24:10–24:16</a></p>\n<h3>Insulting God's representatives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:10-1Kgs21:13\">1KI 21:10–21:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12\">DEU 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:11\">ACT 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>Ignoring God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:30\">NUM 15:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:17\">ISA 63:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:10\">JER 44:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:7\">AMO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:20\">1TH 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Worshipping idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:39\">EZK 20:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:21\">LEV 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:3\">LEV 20:1–20:3</a></p>\n<h3>Sacrificial worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:2\">LEV 22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:6\">LEV 21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:17\">1SA 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6-Mal1:8\">MAL 1:6–1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Towards holy objects and places</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:6-2Sam6:7\">2SA 6:6–6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:7-Ps74:8\">PSA 74:7–74:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:1\">PSA 79:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:30\">JER 7:30</a></p>\n<h3>Attacking God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:7-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:7–22:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:9-2Kgs19:12\">2KI 19:9–19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:16\">2KI 19:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:15-Ps35:16\">PSA 35:15–35:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:10\">PSA 74:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:18\">PSA 74:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:50-Ps89:51\">PSA 89:50–89:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek35:12\">EZK 35:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:8\">DAN 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:21-Dan7:22\">DAN 7:21–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:10-Zeph2:11\">ZEP 2:10–2:11</a>EZK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph36:20-Zeph36:23\">36:20–36:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:24\">ROM 2:24</a></p>\n<h3>Blasphemy against the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:31-Matt12:32\">MAT 12:31–12:32</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:29\">MRK 3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:10\">LUK 12:10</a> <em>Jesus Christ's opponents were beyond hope, so long as they continued to say that the work of the Holy Spirit was the work of Satan (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:24\">Mt 12:24</a>)</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a>JHN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:33\">10:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63-Matt26:65\">MAT 26:63–26:65</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:63-Mark14:64\">MRK 14:63–14:64</a></p>\n<h2>Social consequences of irreverence</h2>\n<h3>In family relationships</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4\">MAT 15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:9\">LEV 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:20\">PRO 20:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:11\">PRO 30:11</a></p>\n<h3>Oppression and cruelty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:9-Ps10:11\">PSA 10:9–10:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:2-Ps73:11\">PSA 73:2–73:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:4-Ps94:7\">PSA 94:4–94:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Social irresponsibility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:16\">JER 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:11-Ezek22:12\">EZK 22:11–22:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:2\">LUK 18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:28–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:20-1Cor11:22\">1CO 11:20–11:22</a></p>\n<h2>Irreverence brings condemnation and judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12-Deut17:13\">DEU 17:12–17:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:19\">PSA 55:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:23\">NUM 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:5\">2CH 26:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16\">2CH 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15-2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:15–36:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:29-Prov1:31\">PRO 1:29–1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:34\">PRO 3:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:14\">PRO 28:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:3\">HOS 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:14\">HOS 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:15\">JUD 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>Particular warnings about the consequences of irreverence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:14-1Sam12:15\">1SA 12:14–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:58-Deut28:59\">DEU 28:58–28:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:1-Mal2:2\">MAL 2:1–2:2</a></p>",
